name: In Search of Monsters
overview: Haunting creatures come to life in a hunt for the truth about infamous monsters and their origins. Experts explore the latest evidence, eyewitness encounters and active investigations while unveiling their mind-blowing theories about these nightmarish beasts.

episodes.name: The Loch Ness Monster
episodes.overview: After centuries of believing the Loch Ness Monster dwells deep within Scotland's Loch Ness, a new theory paints a different story. Experts explore evidence suggesting the monster may not only be real, but possibly more dangerous than ever imagined.

episodes.name: The Wendigo
episodes.overview: Experts explore the legend of the Wendigo, a zombie-like creature doomed in Native American folklore to forever walk alone with its cannibalistic cravings; a new theory suggests this entity may come from somewhere not of this Earth.

episodes.name: Chupacabra
episodes.overview: Shocking new evidence suggests the Chupacabra is hunting humans.

episodes.name: The Yeti
episodes.overview: DNA evidence suggests that the Yeti may have an otherworldly source and also resides in the Americas.

episodes.name: The Beast of Bray Road
episodes.overview: The Beast of Bray Road terrorizes a Wisconsin village, displaying a cunning intelligence and an ability to read minds while hunting its victims; the beast may be multiplying across the United States.

episodes.name: Rock Apes of Vietnam
episodes.overview: New evidence reveals that an American pilot may have returned from Vietnam with a cryptid known as a rock ape.

episodes.name: The Ozark Howler
episodes.overview: Recently disclosed audio recordings and photographs provide the most conclusive evidence to date that the beast with horns known as the Ozark Howler may have demonic origins.

episodes.name: Bigfoot
episodes.overview: Experts reveal all-new evidence and theories related to the world's most famous cryptid -- Bigfoot. Terrifying eyewitness accounts, combined with recently uncovered evidence, unveil a creature far more fierce and predatory than previously believed.

episodes.name: Mothman
episodes.overview: A team of experts and eyewitnesses seek answers about the Mothman, a red-eyed phantom that sours . They explore theories that the legendary cryptid is an abnormality in the evolutionary chain, or even a horrible experiment gone wrong.

episodes.name: The Jersey Devil
episodes.overview: Experts explore the mystery and horror of the Jersey Devil
